---
import PortalShell from "../layouts/PortalShell.astro";
---

<PortalShell activePage="earn" title="分享赚钱" description="申请 FreedomPost 专属分享链接并查看推广数据。">
  <section class="portal-section affiliate-section">
    <div class="portal-container affiliate-layout">
      <div class="affiliate-intro">
        <p class="section-kicker">Affiliate</p>
        <h1>分享赚钱</h1>
        <p>填写微信号即可申请专属链接。通过你的链接进入并确认成交的订单，会按商品设定记录佣金。</p>
        <div class="affiliate-rules">
          <strong>结算规则</strong>
          <span>首次推荐关系永久有效</span>
          <span>确认成交后产生待结算佣金</span>
          <span>当天成交订单当天人工结算</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="affiliate-panel">
        <form id="affiliateAccessForm" class="affiliate-access-form">
          <div>
            <h2>申请或查询</h2>
            <p>首次申请可不填查询密码，系统会自动生成并仅展示一次。</p>
          </div>
          <label><span>微信号</span><input id="affiliateWechatId" name="wechatId" maxlength="32" autocomplete="username" required placeholder="6-32 位字母、数字、下划线或连字符" /></label>
          <label><span>查询密码</span><input id="affiliatePassword" name="password" type="password" maxlength="64" autocomplete="current-password" placeholder="已有专属链接时填写" /></label>
          <button class="button primary" type="submit"><i data-lucide="chart-no-axes-column-increasing"></i>查看推广数据</button>
          <p id="affiliateAccessError" class="form-error" role="alert" hidden></p>
        </form>

        <section id="affiliateDashboard" class="affiliate-dashboard" hidden aria-live="polite">
          <div class="affiliate-dashboard-head">
            <div><p class="section-kicker">Dashboard</p><h2>推广数据</h2></div>
            <button id="affiliateLogout" class="button secondary" type="button">退出查询</button>
          </div>
          <div id="generatedPasswordNotice" class="generated-password" hidden></div>
          <div class="affiliate-link-block">
            <label for="affiliateShareUrl">赚钱专属链接</label>
            <div><input id="affiliateShareUrl" readonly /><button id="copyAffiliateLink" class="button primary" type="button"><i data-lucide="copy"></i>复制分享</button></div>
          </div>
          <div id="affiliateStats" class="affiliate-stats"></div>
          <div class="affiliate-orders-block"><h3>订单与结算记录</h3><div id="affiliateOrders" class="affiliate-order-list"></div></div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PortalShell>
